com.google.android.glass.TMM

Class TextElement

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.android.glass.TMM.TextElement
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class TextElement
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    The Class TextElement. This is used for holding the contents of a text card. This class can either contain a picture and a caption or only text.
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
